<s> Describe the layout and purpose of frames and how multiple frames relate to each other.  </s>
<s> [New] Use the "longdesc" attribute on the FRAME and IFRAME elements to designate a long description.  </s>
<s> If the longdesc attribute should be used to describe how multiple frames relate to each other, why isn't it on the FRAMESET element rather than the FRAME element?  </s>
